{"tid":912638,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高調拉人】央視記者孔琳琳襲擊案　英國檢方證據不足撤控","createTime":"2018-11-23T00:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T02:07:56.000Z","uid":86898,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"17741cbd570d13fada0a54ebebc5083a8d47d2da","tid":912638,"uid":86898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T00:05:17.000Z","msg":"中央電視台記者孔琳琳，在9月底大鬧英國保守黨在伯明翰舉行的「香港自由、法治、自治受損」座談會，更涉嫌掌摑香港義工。英國警方早前以普通襲擊罪起訴她，但央視證實英國當局已撤銷起訴。<br />\n<br />\n央視發言人證實，英國檢方昨（20日）午決定對孔琳琳撤訴，孔琳琳的律師已收到檢方通知。律師表示，檢方重新審查孔琳琳被控普通襲擊罪後，認為證據不足，決定撤銷，原定今日舉行的法庭聽證亦取消。<br />\n<br />\n孔琳琳是央視歐洲中心站記者，今年9月30日在英國保守黨年會一個有關香港事務的座談會上，大聲叫罵與會者「反華」和「漢奸」，並涉嫌掌摑香港留學生義工被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181121/s00004/1542810090475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181121%2Fs00004%2F1542810090475&d=GQ6U6nUhNHM%2B9feMnVYy7rDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=30531439\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181121%2Fs00004%2F1542810090475&h=64bf4840\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181121/s00004/1542810090475</a><br />\n<br />\n大英帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cc767bd9fcbe572fc0cfd17aff83e04a9c3173","tid":912638,"uid":73092,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T00:06:00.000Z","msg":"英國腳軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b006d57e8b7308d6a171a801febfd3b073224f","tid":912638,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T00:06:34.000Z","msg":"呢條八婆就返去做英雄<img src=\"/asset